agenda.description: HOUSE OF REPRESENTATIVES NOTICE OF FORMAL MEETING COMMITTEE: Ways & Means TIME & DATE: upon final adjournment or during reading & referral of bills if permission is granted Tuesday, April 23, 2019 PLACE: Agricultural Museum, 1W.14 CHAIR: Rep.
